<b>Sophos</b> is a developer and vendor of security software and hardware, including <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../622/268622.xml">
anti-virus</link>, <link>
anti-spyware</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../737/313737.xml">
anti-spam</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../627/5913627.xml">
Network Access Control</link> for desktops, servers, email systems and other network gateways.<p>

SophosLabs is the company's global network of threat analysis centers.</p>

